OL,3,C'Heavy cloud descended' in Shantallow
OL,4,Cafter young men die in crash
OL,6,FA "heavy cloud" has descended in the
OL,7,FShantallow area of Londonderry after
OL,8,Fthe deaths of two young men in a road
OL,9,Fcrash in Co Donegal, a parish priest
OL,10,Fhas told UTV.
OL,12,FCaoimhin Porter-McLoone and Daniel
OL,13,FCullen, both 18, were passengers in a
OL,14,Fcar which was in a crash with a lorry
OL,15,Fin the village of St Johnston on
OL,16,FTuesday night.
OL,18,FFr Declan McGeehan described how
OL,19,Futterly devastated the community is
OL,20,Ffollowing the loss.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
