OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772193826
OL,3,C'Heavy cloud descended' in Shantallow
OL,4,Cafter young men die in crash
OL,6,F"Words are inadequate to describe the
OL,7,Ffeeling, ever since the news broke
OL,8,Fthere's just been a heavy cloud that's
OL,9,Fdescended upon the parish," he said.
OL,11,FA third man - understood to be the
OL,12,Fteenagers' friend - is in a serious
OL,13,Fcondition in the Royal Victoria
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FFr McGeehan has been dealing closely
OL,17,Fwith all the families involved.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
