OL,3,C'Heavy cloud descended' in Shantallow
OL,4,Cafter young men die in crash
OL,6,FHe said: "These boys were well known
OL,7,Fin the area, their families live close
OL,8,Ftogether. They were so well known in
OL,9,Fthe community with their schools,
OL,10,Fvarious different groups, so it's
OL,11,Fimpacted so many different people."
